《'''-{zh-cn:修女伊达;zh-tw:依達的抉擇;zh-hk:修女伊德}-'''》（''Ida''）是一部2013年[[帕貝爾·帕夫利柯夫斯基|帕貝爾·帕夫利柯夫斯基]]执导的波兰黑白剧情片，入选2013年[[多伦多影展|多伦多影展]]特别展映单元<ref name="TIFF">{{cite web |url=http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/ida |title=Ida |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130803161754/http://tiff.net/filmsandschedules/festival/2013/ida |archivedate=2013年8月3日 |publisher=[[2013_Toronto_International_Film_Festival|2013 Toronto International Film Festival]] |accessdate=20 June 2014 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>并赢得[[FIPRESCI|FIPRESCI]]特别展映奖<ref name="awards">{{Cite news |url=http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/tiff/2013/09/15/tiff_2013_12_years_a_slave_wins_top_prize_at_film_fest.html |title=TIFF 2013: 12 Years a Slave wins film fest's top prize |work=[[Toronto_Star|Toronto Star]] |agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |date=15 September 2013 |accessdate=20 June 2014 |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006102020/http://www.thestar.com/entertainment/tiff/2013/09/15/tiff_2013_12_years_a_slave_wins_top_prize_at_film_fest.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。代表波兰角逐第87届[[奥斯卡最佳外语片|奥斯卡最佳外语片]]<ref name="87th">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-poland-anoints-ida-as-candidate-for-foreign-language-academy-award-1201279451/ |title=Oscars: Poland Anoints ‘Ida’ as Candidate for Foreign-Language Academy Award |accessdate=11 August 2014 |work=Variety |archive-date=2015-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150423060618/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/oscars-poland-anoints-ida-as-candidate-for-foreign-language-academy-award-1201279451/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。获得第27届[[欧洲电影奖|欧洲电影奖]][[歐洲電影獎最佳影片獎|最佳影片獎]]、最佳导演、最佳编剧等五项大奖<ref>{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/ida-leviathan-top-european-film-awards-nominations-1201351250/ |title=‘Ida,’ ‘Leviathan’ Top European Film Awards Nominations |accessdate=9 November 2014 |work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304094613/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/ida-leviathan-top-european-film-awards-nominations-1201351250/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/european-film-awards-2014-winners-full-list-1201323275/ |title=European Film Awards: 'Ida' Best Picture; Timothy Spall, Marion Cotillard Top Actors |accessdate=13 December 2014 |work=Deadline |archive-date=2019-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616173930/https://deadline.com/2014/12/european-film-awards-2014-winners-full-list-1201323275/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，第16届[[波兰电影奖|波兰电影奖]]最佳影片、导演、女主角和剪辑四个大奖，以及[[第68届英国电影学院奖|第68届英国电影学院奖]]和[[第87届奥斯卡金像奖|第87届奥斯卡金像奖]]最佳外语片，这是第十次提名奥斯卡最佳外语片的[[波兰电影|波兰电影]]，以及首次获奖的波兰作品。

==剧情==
故事发生在1960年代的[[波兰|波兰]]。<ref name=stevens>{{cite web |url=http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/movies/2014/05/ida_review_pawel_pawlikowski_s_hauntingly_beautiful_road_movie_is_finally.html |last=Stevens |first=Dana |authorlink=Dana Stevens (critic) |title=Ida: A journey you won’t forget |date=2 May 2014 |accessdate=2014-05-05 |work=Slate |archive-date=2018-07-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180710213022/http://www.slate.com/articles/arts/movies/2014/05/ida_review_pawel_pawlikowski_s_hauntingly_beautiful_road_movie_is_finally.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>安娜是一名在[[修道院|修道院]]长大的[[孤儿|孤儿]]，在宣誓正式成为[[修女|修女]]之前，她必须要见到家人。离开修道院后，她见到了活着的唯一亲人——姨妈旺达。旺达告诉安娜说她父母是[[犹太人|犹太人]]，并且已经在战争中（[[二战|二战]][[纳粹德军|纳粹德军]]占领波兰期间）遇难，而安娜的原名是伊达。安娜决定陪伴姨妈去一起寻找父母的墓地。

