==评价==
[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]上依据109篇评论持有95%的新鲜度<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ida_2013/|title=Ida|date=2 May 2014|publisher=|accessdate=21 October 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012401/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/ida_2013|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上34篇影评得分89分<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/ida|title=Ida Reviews - Metacritic|publisher=|accessdate=21 October 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112012926/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/ida|dead-url=no}}</ref>，获得广泛赞誉。

==票房==
[[北美|北美]]收获超过360万美元的成绩，位居年度票房外语片的前列<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nun-drama-ida-is-polands-726199|title=Nun Drama 'Ida' Is Poland's Oscar Candidate|author=Scott Roxborough|date=19 August 2014|work=The Hollywood Reporter|accessdate=21 October 2014|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112000350/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/nun-drama-ida-is-polands-726199|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[法国|法国]]大约有50万人进场观看了该片，成为法国票房最好的一部[[波兰语|波兰语]]电影。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telerama.fr/cinema/l-incroyable-succes-du-film-ida-aussi-aux-etats-unis,118647.php |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2014-12-02 |archive-date=2016-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160419024809/http://www.telerama.fr/cinema/l-incroyable-succes-du-film-ida-aussi-aux-etats-unis,118647.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>

